## Summary
Add 1 test case for Payload_MultiPart_FormData_anonymousModel to existing multipart test file.

## Fix
Add test in `test/e2e/http/payload/multipart/main.test.ts`:
```typescript
it('should send multipart request with anonymous model', async () => {
  await client.formData.anonymousModel({
    profileImage: createFilePartDescriptor('profileImage', jpegContents, 'image/jpeg'),
  });
});
```

## Notes
- The spec defines an inline body type `{ profileImage: HttpPart<bytes> }` instead of a named model
- Verify the generated client has the anonymousModel method
